# MyWeatherToday — Environment Variables
#
# This app uses exclusively FREE, keyless APIs:
#
#   Open-Meteo Weather   → https://api.open-meteo.com        (no key needed)
#   Open-Meteo Geocoding → https://geocoding-api.open-meteo.com (no key needed)
#   Nominatim Reverse    → https://nominatim.openstreetmap.org  (no key needed)
#
# No environment variables are required to run or deploy this application.
# Copy this file to .env.local if you ever add paid API integrations in the future.
#
# Example (not currently used):
# WEATHER_API_KEY=your_key_here
